title: EZ CD Audio Converter 2.7.0.1 Multilang
description:
EZ CD Audio Converter is the most comprehensive multi format audio converter and is extremely easy to use. Rips audio CDs, 

converts audio files, allows editing of metadata, and burns discs. It has efficient error-detective CD-ripping, very fast 

parallel audio conversion, and reliable disc burning. All combined to user friendly, beautiful interface.

Changelog:
Cover Art downloader - search & download Cover Art from GD3 and MusicBrainz
FLAC, Vorbis, Opus metadata changes:
Total tracks written to TRACKTOTAL instead of TRACKNUMBER X/Y
Total discs written to DISCTOTAL instead of DISCNUMBER X/Y
Addtional Cue Sheet properties: GENRE, DATE, DISCID, MBDISCID, TOC, and COMMENT
LibOgg 1.3.2 updated to FLAC, Vorbis, and Opus codecs
Improved Internet download library (stability improvements on connection errors)

OS: Windows 8, 7, Vista, and XP
Home Page: www.poikosoft.com
Interface: Multilang
